description: Test conventions for this project
alwaysApply: true
---

# Test Coverage

- Unit tests live in a `#[cfg(test)] mod tests` block at the bottom of each source file
- Integration tests live in `tests/` and cover end-to-end flows (e.g. pcm -> transcript, transcript -> markdown)
- Audio/model tests that require hardware use `#[ignore]` so `cargo test` passes in CI without devices
- Test names describe behavior: `transcribes_silence_as_empty`, not `test1`
- Use `insta` or inline snapshots for markdown output tests
